text: Lamona is an unincorporated community located in southern Lincoln County, Washington, United States, between Odessa and Harrington on State Route 28. Lamona is located at an elevation of above sea level. Lamona was named for its first merchant, in 1892–1893, J.H. Lamona. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Washington (state) Category:Unincorporated communities in Lincoln County, Washington
